headline: Cohesity Recognized as "Top Durable Growth and Innovation Partner, FY25" in Cisco SolutionsPlus Program
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., December 04, 2025--Cohesity, the leader in AI-powered data security, today announced that the company was named the "Top Durable Growth and Innovation Partner for FY25" amongst partners in the Cisco SolutionsPlus program.

headline: OECD-Cisco research finds stark geographical and generational divides in AI uptake and digital well-being
summary: Generative AI is moving rapidly from novelty to habit. But adoption rates may not tell the full story. Cisco, the worldwide leader in networking and security, partnered with the Organisation for Economic Cooperation and Development (OECD) on the Digital Well-being Hub to study the relationship between technology's risks and benefits, and how AI is impacting people's lives. New data from the Hub reveals that, beneath the headlines of youthful enthusiasm for AI, geographic and generational divides

headline: 1 Growth Stock with All-Star Potential and 2 We Question
summary: Growth is oxygen. But when it evaporates, the consequences can be severe - ask anyone who bought Cisco in the Dot-Com Bubble or newer investors who lived through the 2020 to 2022 COVID cycle.
